text:
The magazine we shot for
the other day is finally out!

Hehe... I was nervous during the shoot,
but looking at this photo, I don't feel that way at all.

Thanks to Luca-chan's guidance,
I feel like we achieved this kind of atmosphere...

…?
I didn't really do anything special though...

No, I also,
feel like Luca-chan guided us.

Hehe...! I'm looking forward
to seeing everyone's reactions to the magazine...!
